## Tooling (Claude Code skills)

- Edit `SKILL.md` (the skill's instructions + trigger description) and add supporting files alongside it.
- `.claude-plugin/plugin.json` is the plugin manifest. Keep `name` and `version` current.
- `python3 scripts/validate-skill.py` checks SKILL.md frontmatter and plugin.json — CI runs the same.
- No runtime/test toolchain: this package ships prose + assets, not compiled code.
